					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If there's no mapper, the mirroring is set using solder pads that hardwire PA10 or PA11 to A10 in. You set the mirroring by bridging one pair of pads and not bridging the other pair.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

